---
title: Chicken in Creamy Mushroom Sauce with softened leeks and fluffy rice
description: There are many reasons this creamy chicken in mushroom sauce is the perfect weeknight meal. Not only is it super speedy to make, it's also made up of those favourite flavours your whole house is sure to love.
